Dialogs.Dialog: ...Don't you get it？ You've been a little cold lately.
Huh？ Maybe I am in a bad groove.
Just get your groove on or something. You've got to do better than that.
(Well, she's in a bad mood today. Yes, I may have been cold lately...)
I'm so sorry, I won't do it again！
...You know you're in the wrong, right？
Please, return to your happy self.
It can't be helped. I'm your girlfriend after all...
Well, get yourself in a good mood.
...Just this once. Just this once, so don't get carried away.
(You've forgiven me, right？ I feel like you're not quite convinced...)
What's wrong with you？ How are you as a boyfriend these days？
Um... are you in a bad mood？
It's not Rinko's mood that's bad, it's your attitude.
(This is serious... Yes, I may have been cold lately...)
I'm so sorry, I won't do it again！
...You know you did a bad thing, right？
Come on, get back in a good mood.
Ah, geez, no. I won't do it！
Why not？ Come on, it's all good.
Well, get yourself in a good mood.
I don't want to forgive... I won't forgive you, geez... I forgive you.
I forgive you！ I said I forgive you...
(You've forgiven me, right？ I feel like you're not quite convinced...)
Is it my imagination？ Lately, I feel like you're giving me the cold shoulder.
Eh... Uh, you're not imagining things, are you？
Please. Answer me again, and answer me properly.
(You sound like you mean it... You're right, maybe I've been cold lately...)
I'm so sorry, I won't do it again！
..You know you're in the wrong, right？
Come on, get back in a good mood.
Because it doesn't make me any less anxious...
Well, get yourself in a good mood.
...It can't be helped. If you've been together long enough, things like this happen.
Oh. I've heard something like that. So it's okay this time, right？
Yeah... because it can't be helped.
(You've forgiven me, right？ I feel like you're not quite convinced...)
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
(She might still be mad at me, so it's fine...)
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
(She might still be mad at me, so it's fine...)
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
Rinko is not in the mood yet.
(She might still be mad at me, so it's fine...)
Let's go on a date, ▲小早川＊▲.
Let's go on a date, ▲小早川＊▲.
No. I don't want to go.
(It's a phone call... Ah, are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲？)
You know, about the date we promised before...
I want to cancel. See you.
(It's a phone call... Ah, are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲？)
About our date, we won't have one.
See you, my business here is done.
(It's a phone call... Ah, are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲？)
Hey, we have a date coming up. You remember, right？
I see. But I want to cancel that one. Later.
Listen, can we meet now, ▲小早川＊▲？
I can't see you now. I can't see you in the future... Like that.
Listen, can we meet now, ▲小早川＊▲？
Listen, can we meet now, ▲小早川＊▲？
He's trying so hard. He looks like an idiot.
Even in times like these, he doesn't cut corners.
That doesn't make any sense whatsoever.
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
(Are you still mad at me, ▲小早川＊▲...？)
I don't have anything to say.
Yeah, I know. You're doing your best.
It's because it was hard. I couldn't talk to you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Geez, that's enough. No more of this. Geez, no more.
...That's the only way to do it.
You're trying too hard. And that's okay.
Yeah, I was thinking on a way you could forgive me, ▲小早川＊▲...
Too extreme. You just need to do better on a regular basis.
That's okay. I've done enough to get back at you... This is enough.
Oh, geez, you idiot. Don't think I've forgiven you for this.
I was watching. You did it for Rinko.
I wanted to make up with you as soon as possible, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yeah, thanks. Rinko was already at the end of her rope.
It's only natural. How can you not be lonely？
I'm sorry. I won't let you go through that again.
Huh？ Why...？ Um, come on in.
I'm here to visit you. Have you been a good girl？
What's do you mean with good girl. You came out of nowhere...
Much better now. I was bored, so it was just as well.
Sorry, this is taking so long. I'm going to go home now.
That's not what I meant. But thanks, just in case.
Eh, wait for a bit！ ...Okay, come on in.
Well, yeah. You exaggerate visiting me.
It's not a nuisance... Thanks for taking the time.
(You're being honest... Is it because of your illness？)
It's okay, sometimes. I was really kind of happy.
(Did you see it on my face...？)
It's been quite a while. I'm about to leave, but can I come back？
You don't have to ask every time.
I see. Well, then. Get well soon.
Eh？ You can't come in！ ...Now it's okay.
Yeah, I'm much better now. I was bored.
Yeah... Hehe, you came to visit me, right？
I should go home. It's bad if I stay too long.
That's not how it works. First of all, you have to get well.
Yeah. So, you'll have to endure today. Bye.
But we can't leave the room.
That's where you need to go. Go convince mom.
Don't be selfish. You look fine, but you're still sick.
Hey, you've been coming to visit me a lot. Aren't you busy？
I'll come even if I'm not busy.
Ah, geez, shut up！ I don't need to know that.
Hey, are you that worried about Rinko？ Do you want her to get better soon？
Hehe, I just wanted to ask.
You're overreacting. It's just a cold, right？
If it gets complicated, it will be hard. It would make me happy if you were more honest.
I can't help it. Anxious old man.
You can tell by looking at me, can't you？
Haha, yes. It's a full recovery.
And, hey, thanks for your visit, just in case.
Hmm？ Oh, don't worry about that. I'm glad you're better.
Let me worry about it. I was happy.
Yeah. I'm sure it's because of your visit, huh？
Haha, is that so？ You were very quiet back then, ▲小早川＊▲.
Because, you know, I can't wait to have fun.
But you know, first I want to have fun with you, you know？
(I'm bored... I'm tired of staying home.)
I wonder who it is... Coming！
Yes, a visit. In case you're wondering, I'm your girlfriend, you know？
Thanks for coming all the way home.
The sick should not care about that.
Haha, I see. But I'm glad you came, I was bored.
Oh, it's already this late. I better go home.
Can you stay a little longer？
I would love to, but... I'd hate to make it worse.
Get well soon. You're not the only one who has free time because of your illness.
(For your sake, I have to get better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(I'm bored... I'm tired of staying home.)
I wonder who it is... Coming！
I was surprised. I didn't think you would come.
I thought it would be more gratifying. I'm glad you're doing well.
I'm going home soon. And you should get some rest.
You don't have to be so careful.
I won't get sick. I'm used to deal with sick people.
Yeah. I don't think it's a good idea to worry too much about your girlfriend, do you？
(For your sake, I have to get better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(I'm bored... I'm tired of staying home.)
I wonder who it is... Coming！
I was getting bored. I'm glad.
Well, so-so. It's a lot easier now.
Sorry, I stayed too long. I'm going home now.
Oh, thanks. That was really helpful.
Is there anything else you need help with？ Like your housework, or the like.
Eh, it's okay. You're against time.
...Don't look so anxious. If things get really bad, call me. Bye.
(For your sake, I have to get better soon, ▲小早川＊▲.)
No way. I'm glad you're here.
Hmm... That's another one of the boyfriends' prerogatives.
You're a lucky guy. You have a kind girlfriend who comes to visit you when you get sick.
Oh, I'm a happy man. I have no more regrets...
Huh, doesn't that make you feel sad？
No, it doesn't. If I ever find myself in that situation, I'll kick you for leaving Rinko alone.
Hey, is there anything you want to do？
Hey, my ass. Wait until you're healed before you do that.
If you're so frustrated, you should get well soon.
Thanks for your visit. Thanks to you, I'm back.
I'm in a bad mood from all the free time I had while I was sick. You should have get well sooner.
Thanks to you, I'm back to full strength. I can dodge a kick now, can't I？
You must take care of Rinko for all the time you were sick！
I'm all better now. Thanks to your visit, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe, yay. Then take me on a date in return.
Yeah, I know. What should I do...？
Hey, hey, when do you want to do it？
